{{! This handlebar is designed to convert Spells exported from Foundry.  It relies on two modules, PF2E Exporter and More Handlebars Helpers.}}
---
obsidianUIMode: preview
title: "{{{name}}}"
noteType: pf2eSpell
cssclasses:
  - pf2e
  - pf2e-spell
tags:
  - pf2eSpell
  - spell/level/{{system.level.value}}
  {{#each system.traits.value}}
  - trait/{{this}}
   {{/each}}
  - trait/{{system.traits.rarity}}
  {{#if system.traits.traditions}}
  {{#each system.traits.traditions}}
  - tradition/{{this}}
  {{/each}}
  {{/if}}

{{#if system.ritual}}
  - ritual
{{/if~}}
{{#if system.publication.remaster}}
  - remaster
{{/if~}}
aliases:
  - "{{{uuid}}}" 
license: {{system.publication.license}}
---
# {{{name}}} {{#if actionGlyph}} {{{me-actionIcon system.time.value}}}{{/if}} _{{#if isRitual}}Ritual{{else}}{{#if isCantrip}}Cantrip{{else}}{{#if isFocusSpell}}Focus{{else}}Spell{{/if}}{{/if}}{{/if}} {{system.level.value}}_

> [!pf2e-traits]
> - {{{ more-handlebars-helpers-table system.traits.rarity "common" "" "uncommon" "[[Uncommon]]" "rare" "[[Rare]]" "unique" "[[Unique]]"}}}
{{#each system.traits.value as |trait index|}}
> - [[{{trait}}]]
{{/each}}

{{#if system.traits.traditions}}
- Traditions :: {{#each system.traits.traditions}}{{this}}{{ifThen @last "" ", "}}{{/each}}
{{/if}}
{{~#if (or (not actionGlyph) (or system.cost.value system.ritual.secondary.casters))}}
- Cast :: {{{me-actionIcon system.time.value}}}
{{~#if system.cost.value~}}
- Cost :: {{{system.cost.value}}}
{{~/if~}}
{{~#if system.ritual.secondary.casters~}}
- Secondary Casters :: {{system.ritual.secondary.casters}}
{{~/if~}}
{{/if}}
{{#if system.ritual.primary.check}}
- Primary Check :: {{system.ritual.primary.check}}
{{~/if~}}
{{#if system.ritual.secondary.checks~}}
- Secondary Checks :: {{system.ritual.secondary.checks}}
{{~/if~}}{{#if system.range.value}}
- Range :: {{system.range.value}}
{{/if}}{{#if system.area.value}}
- Area :: {{system.area.value}}-foot {{system.area.type}}
{{/if}}{{#if system.target.value}}
- Targets :: {{system.target.value}}
{{/if}}{{#if system.defense.save}}
- Defense :: {{#if system.defense.save.basic}}basic{{/if}} {{system.defense.save.statistic}}
{{/if~}}
{{#if system.duration.value}}
- Duration :: {{system.duration.value}}
{{/if}}

{{{me-HTMLtoMarkdown system.description.value this}}}

Source :: {{{system.publication.title}}}
